\par }{\b\fs26\lang1033\langfe1031\langnp1033 What}{\fs26\lang1033\langfe1031\langnp1033 
\par }{\fs22\lang1033\langfe1031\langnp1033 
\par Often needed functions and extensions when working with VB forms in a fully self-contained
\par }{\b\fs22\lang1033\langfe1031\langnp1033 usercontrol}{\fs22\lang1033\langfe1031\langnp1033  (thx&credits to Paul Caton! - no more bas file(s), IDE crash or anything else on subclassing).
\par 
\par 
\par   *  Restrict forms size (min/max) flickerfree.
\par   *  Get much more events (app activate/deactivate, resize start/end, move start/end, ... )
\par   *  Save/restore forms last size/position to registry or INI file (still yet:  No line of code ... ;) )
\par   *  Two more buttons in forms caption bar :
\par \tab \tab 1 - Collapse to headline/restore to previous size
\par \tab \tab 2 - Stay on top of all other windows
\par   *  Form resizing with auto keep aspect ratio.
\par   *  A simple and vary good solution to resize/reposition controls on form when resizing the form.
\par   *  Drag form full or frame only independent to control panels setting.
\par   *  Center/resize form to useable desktop area with respect to all taskbars. A gap to the borders can be given.
\par   *  Show form without activation.
\par   *  Some usefull properties.
\par   *  And more ...
\par 
\par All of this features are switchable/configurable on design time in WizzForms usercontrol
\par property window. No line of code neccessary!
\par Switch them on or off, single (or all together with the 'Enabled' property).
\par 
\par 
\par }{\b\fs26\lang1033\langfe1031\langnp1033 What not
